<view class="page"><view class="hero"><view class="title">提交本次作业</view><view class="muted">中途退出会保留草稿；网络恢复后使用同一操作编号继续，不会重复创建版本。</view></view><view wx:if="{{error}}" class="card error">{{error}}</view><view class="card"><textarea class="field" placeholder="补充文字说明" value="{{text}}" bindinput="input"/><view class="buttonRow"><button class="secondary" bindtap="choose">照片/短视频</button><button class="secondary" bindtap="chooseDocument">PDF/Word</button><button class="secondary" bindtap="toggleRecord">{{recording?'停止录音':'录制语音'}}</button></view><view wx:for="{{files}}" wx:key="tempFilePath" class="uploadRow"><view><b>{{item.name}}</b><text>{{item.status==='uploaded'?'已上传':item.status==='uploading'?'上传 '+item.progress+'%':item.status==='failed'?item.error:'待上传'}}</text></view><button wx:if="{{item.status==='failed'}}" size="mini" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="retry">重试</button><button wx:else size="mini" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="remove">移除</button></view><view class="muted">已选择 {{files.length}} 个文件；首次和每次订正版都会保留。</view></view><button class="primary fixedAction" loading="{{busy}}" disabled="{{busy||(!text&&!files.length)}}" bindtap="submit">确认最终提交</button></view>
